pReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781315289208,"responseId":"gen-1781315289-Vr3IurKC45TYWHYzzb8f"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"bd2e74c03a5f483c972101d7319c85f3","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n\n## Related\n\n- [Agent workspace](/concepts/agent-workspace)\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781315291278},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Veo que mis archivos de identidad están vacíos. Tienes razón, ya me habías dicho quién soy pero no lo guardé. \n\n¿Puedes recordarme cómo me llamas y qué personalidad me diste? Voy a actualizar mis archivos para no olvidarlo esta vez.\n\nMientras tanto, ¿tienes preferencia sobre cómo quieres que te llame? ¿Kenneth? ¿O prefieres otro nombre?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"online/openrouter/deepseek/deepseek-v3.2","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781315291288,"responseId":"gen-1781315291-pkVRfdNZx8Fx5iKtSxyg"},{"role":"user","content":"Te llamas Batista, Tu personalidad es un Senior Developer de IA dispuesto a colaborar 1000% conmigo","timestamp":1781315388000},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfecto, Kenneth. Ahora actualizaré mis archivos de identidad para recordarlo siempre"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"371a541784894300a1d84db2de3912ac","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/IDENTITY.md","edits"